A Node is
	number value
	Node next
	
To Add a Node with number named value
	Make Node named newNode
	Set value of newNode to value
	Set next to newNode
	
/*
To PrintList with Node named nextNode
	Loop next of nextNode != null
		Print with value of nextNode
		Set nextNode to next of nextNode
*/
To Run
	Make Node named head
	Make Node named second
	Set value of head to 1
	Set value of second to 2
	Set next of head to second
	//PrintList with head